"modified sales price equal to the original sales price plus the tax amount."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:403
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax with :guilabel:`Affect base of "
"subsequent taxes`. Any subsequent tax with :guilabel:`Base affected by "
"preceding taxes` will be based on a modified sales price of $1100."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:409
