msgid ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`, :guilabel:`Bill Reference`, :guilabel:`Bill "
"Date`, :guilabel:`Payment Reference` (only in the Belgian +++xxx/xxxx/xxxxx++"
"+ format), :guilabel:`Recipient Bank`, :guilabel:`Due Date`, and the "
"currency (in a :doc:`multi-currency <../get_started/multi_currency>` "
"environment and if the currency is activated)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vendor`, :guilabel:`Bill Reference`, :guilabel:`Bill "
"Date`, :guilabel:`Payment Reference` (только в бельгийском формате +++xxx/"
"xxxx/xxxxx+++), :guilabel:`Recipient Bank`, :guilabel:`Due Date` и валюта "
"(в :doc:`мультивалютной <../get_started/multi_currency>` среде и если валюта "
"активирована)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:116
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Invoices Lines` tab: :guilabel:`Product` description/"
"label, :guilabel:`Quantity`, unit :guilabel:`Price`, :guilabel:`Taxes` (if "
"the :ref:`tax is activated <taxes/list_activation>`; this field is not "
"recognized by OCR for the :doc:`Indian localization <../../"
"fiscal_localizations/india>`), :guilabel:`Untaxed Amount`, "
"and :guilabel:`Total`."
msgstr ""
"На вкладке :guilabel:`Invoices Lines`: описание/"
"обозначение :guilabel:`Product`, :guilabel:`Quantity`, :guilabel:`Price` за "
"единицу, :guilabel:`Taxes` (если :ref:`налог активирован <taxes/"
"list_activation>`; это поле не распознаётся OCR для :doc:`индийской "
"локализации <../../fiscal_localizations/india>`), :guilabel:`Untaxed Amount` "
"и :guilabel:`Total`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:125
msgid "Vendor bill matching with purchase orders"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:127
msgid ""
"When a digitized vendor bill is recognized by OCR, Odoo first searches the "
"database for a matching purchase order and its number. If a match is found, "
"the system copies as much information as possible from the purchase order to "
"the vendor bill. For example, the vendor :guilabel:`Bill Reference` number "
"is overwritten by the :guilabel:`Vendor Reference` from the purchase order."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:133
msgid "All changes are logged in the chatter."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:134
msgid ""
"A smart button linking to the related purchase order is available on the "
"vendor bill."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:136
msgid ""
"To correct any mismatches, update the incorrect fields on the vendor bill."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:139
msgid ""
"Electronic vendor bills with embedded XML ensure more accurate and efficient "
"processing."
msgstr ""
"Электронные счета поставщиков со встроенным XML обеспечивают более точную и "
"эффективную обработку."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:140
msgid ""
"Alternatively, the :ref:`Auto-complete <accounting/vendor_bills/bill-"
"completion>` feature can be used to transfer information from the purchase "
"order to the vendor bill, without requiring OCR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:149
msgid ""
"The document digitization feature is an In-App Purchase (IAP) service "
"requiring prepaid credits. Digitizing one document uses one credit."
msgstr ""
"Функция оцифровки документов является услугой внутрипрограммных покупок "
"(IAP), требующей предоплаченных кредитов. Оцифровка одного документа "
"использует один кредит."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:152
msgid ""
"To buy credits, :ref:`go to the Settings app <iap/buying_credits>` "
"or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Digitization` section, and click :guilabel:`Buy credits`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы купить кредиты, :ref:`перейдите в приложение «Настройки» <iap/"
"buying_credits>` или :menuselection:`Бухгалтерский учёт --> Конфигурация --> "
"Настройки`, перейдите к разделу :guilabel:`Оцифровка` и "
"нажмите :guilabel:`Купить кредиты`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:157
msgid ""
"Odoo Enterprise users with a valid subscription get free credits to test IAP "
"features before purchasing more credits for the database. This includes demo/"
"training databases, educational databases, and one-app-free databases."
msgstr ""
"Пользователи Odoo Enterprise с действующей подпиской получают бесплатные "
"кредиты для тестирования функций IAP перед покупкой дополнительных кредитов "
"для базы данных. Это включает демонстрационные/обучающие базы данных, "
"образовательные базы данных и базы данных с бесплатным одним приложением."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:160
msgid ""
"XML files don't require OCR credits because they contain structured data "
"that can be processed directly, without OCR."
msgstr ""
"XML-файлы не требуют кредитов OCR, поскольку они содержат структурированные "
"данные, которые могут обрабатываться напрямую, без OCR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:164
msgid ""
"`Odoo In-App Purchase Privacy Policy <https://iap.odoo.com/"
"privacy#header_6>`_"
msgstr ""
