#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reimburse.rst:5
msgid ""
"After an expense report is :doc:`posted to an accounting journal <../"
"expenses/post_expenses>`, the next step is to reimburse the employee. Just "
"like approving and posting expenses, employees can be reimbursed in two "
"ways: with cash, check, or direct deposit (:ref:`individually <expenses/"
"reimburse-single>` or :ref:`in bulk <expenses/reimburse-bulk>`), "
"or :ref:`reimbursed in a payslip <expenses/reimburse-payslip>`."
