"essentials/in_app_purchase>` to compute the taxes and to send the electronic "
"invoices. Whenever you compute taxes, send an electronic document (NF-e, NFS-"
"e, etc), or perform any electronic flow (NF-e Cancellation, Correction "
"letter, Invalidate invoice number range), an API call is made using credits "
"from your `IAP credits balance <https://iap.odoo.com/iap/in-app-services/"
"819>`_."
