#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/amazon_payment_services.rst:13
msgid ""
"Log into your `Amazon Payment Services Dashboard <https://fort.payfort.com/"
">`_ and go to :menuselection:`Integration Settings --> Security Settings`. "
"Generate the :guilabel:`Access Code` if none has been generated yet. Copy "
"the values of the :guilabel:`Merchant Identifier`, :guilabel:`Access "
"Code`, :guilabel:`SHA Request Phrase` and :guilabel:`SHA Response Phrase` "
"fields, and save them for later."
msgstr ""
"Войдите в свою `панель управления Amazon Payment Services <https://"
"fort.payfort.com/>`_ и перейдите в :menuselection:`Integration Settings --> "
"Security Settings`. Сгенерируйте :guilabel:`Access Code`, если он еще не был "
"создан. Скопируйте значения полей :guilabel:`Merchant "
"Identifier`, :guilabel:`Access Code`, :guilabel:`SHA Request Phrase` "
"и :guilabel:`SHA Response Phrase` и сохраните их для дальнейшего "
"использования."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/amazon_payment_services.rst:18
msgid ""
"Enter your Odoo database URL in the :guilabel:`Origin URL`, for example: "
"`https://yourcompany.odoo.com/`. Then, click on :guilabel:`Save Changes`."
msgstr ""
"Введите URL-адрес вашей базы данных Odoo в поле :guilabel:`Origin URL`, "
"например: `https://yourcompany.odoo.com/`. Затем нажмите :guilabel:`Save "
"Changes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/amazon_payment_services.rst:20
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Integration Settings --> Technical Settings` and "
"click on :guilabel:`Redirection`. Make sure :guilabel:`Status` is set to "
"`Active` and select your preferred payment methods underneath "
"in :guilabel:`Payment Options`."
msgstr ""
"Перейдите в :menuselection:`Integration Settings --> Technical Settings` и "
"нажмите :guilabel:`Redirection`. Убедитесь, что :guilabel:`Status` "
"установлен в `Active`, и выберите предпочитаемые способы оплаты ниже в "
"разделе :guilabel:`Payment Options`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/amazon_payment_services.rst:0
msgid ""
"Set :guilabel:`Send Response Parameters` to :guilabel:`Yes` and enter your "
"database URL followed by `/payment/aps/return` in the :guilabel:`Redirection "
"URL`."
msgstr ""
"Установите :guilabel:`Send Response Parameters` в значение :guilabel:`Yes` и "
"введите URL-адрес вашей базы данных, за которым следует `/payment/aps/"
"return`, в поле :guilabel:`Redirection URL`."

